7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"ISO 22000- Food Safety Management- Organizations Must Know"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:31:02+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"The standards of a Food Safety Management System are outlined in the international standard Food Safety Certification (ISO 22000:2015)."}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 22000- Food Safety Management- Organizations Must Know"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The standards of a Food Safety Management System are outlined in the international standard Food Safety Certification (ISO 22000:2015). For every organization in the food sector, it is a crucial standard. Risk-based thinking is used in the ISO Certification process. For businesses in the food and beverage industry, it is an essential prerequisite."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Advantages of ISO 22000 Food Safety Management System"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The organisation will gain a great deal from having ISO 22000 Food Safety Management System. Expanding the business and acquiring new clients is one of its numerous benefits."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The best practices outlined in the ISO Standard will also guarantee food safety and uphold quality throughout. It guarantees that the business complies with government standards on food safety. Additionally, food safety and quality maintenance will be guaranteed by the ISO Standard best practices. It guarantees that the business complies with ISO certification standards in UAE for food industry set forth by the government. Food Management System guarantees:"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Increased supervision of food safety initiatives"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Observance of regulations and food safety guidelines"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Gaining the trust of customers will help the market flourish."}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Integration with other ISO Management Systems and risk assessment. Become well-known worldwide for your company"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Regardless of size or nature, all organisations must adhere to the Food Safety Management Standard. The ISO Certification Dubai is advantageous to all businesses operating within the food chain. For the food industry to ensure that all safety goals are met, this accreditation is crucial. Additionally, the company can consistently attract more happy clients."}],["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 22000 Certification UAE- HACCP Control Checks"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Process control points and hazard assessments at different production phases make up the Food Safety Management Standard. The supply chain is dotted with control sites. It seeks to increase team accountability and bring openness to the system as a whole. The Hazard Analysis and Critical Control Point tests, together with the ISO 9001 QMS method to Quality Management, are combined in the food safety standard. Food safety is guaranteed on all fronts thanks to the certification."}],"$L10","$L11"]}],"$L12"]}]}]
