10:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"As a result, companies who obtain certification may show that they have the capacity to manage safety risks and guarantee that food is always safe. Food safety is a major global issue, and it's critical to prevent any illnesses or injuries brought on by eating food."}]
11:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Get ISO Certification in UAE, Dubai, Abu Dhabi, and Sharjah with our ISO certification consultants within 4-6 weeks. WIZMS offers ISO 9001, 45001, 14001, 22000, 27001 and other standards."}]
